android.provider
Class Checkin

java.lang.Object
  android.provider.Checkin

public final class Checkin
extends Object

Contract class for CheckinProvider. Describes the exposed database schema, and offers methods to add events and statistics to be uploaded.

Nested Class Summary
static interface Checkin.Crashes
          The crashes table is a log of crash reports, kept separate from the general event log because crashes are large, important, and bursty.
static interface Checkin.Events
          The events table is a log of important timestamped occurrences.
static interface Checkin.Properties
          The properties table is a set of tagged values sent with every checkin.
static interface Checkin.Stats
          The stats table is a list of counter values indexed by a tag name.
static interface Checkin.TriggerIntent
          Intents with this action cause a checkin attempt.
